# Eval cases for Agentic RAG retrieval quality (PR0 baseline).
#
# Each line is a JSON object with:
#   case_id             - unique identifier
#   query               - natural language query
#   expected_doc_ids    - file URLs / doc_ids that should appear in top results
#   expected_categories - categories results should match
#   min_hits            - minimum expected_doc_ids required (default 1)
#   top_k               - number of results to retrieve (default 5)
#   notes               - human-readable explanation
#
# Category-only cases (no expected_doc_ids, with expected_categories):
#   The evaluator requires at least 1 category hit to pass.
#   Place cases that cannot yet match any category with empty expected_categories
#   and min_hits=0 — they document unsupported features without failing.
#
